item.title: A Recent 3D Printing Breakthrough Brings Us One Step Closer to You Downloading a Car
item.description: Researchers at MIT successfully printed a working motor in a just few hours.

item.title: NASA Delays Launch of Artemis II Lunar Mission Once Again
item.description: A failure in the helium flow of the SLS rocket has prompted NASA to delay the Artemis II moon mission. Rather than March 6, the launch is now targeted for April.
